r Interface，BCI）技術可以將晶片直接植入到抑鬱症病人身體裏。有關晶片能將大腦中的訊號通過藍牙無限傳輸到電腦中實時記錄，神經外科醫生再用人工智能技術分析出病人的問題。通過神經訊號的變化，利用電刺激反饋給予相應的刺激治療，可以將抑鬱症狀扼殺在搖籃中。<br />\n<br />\n目前，該研究已通過倫理審查，正在招募18歲以上難治性抑鬱症患者接受試驗。<br />\n<br />\nSource: 01"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:34:30.000Z","msg":"Chinapunk 2027"},{"pid":"775db0f894c56d7cb657ac9cfd9c81a3eb7d3cc4","tid":2324855,"uid":49136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:34:40.000Z","msg":"好快會用晶片「醫」反對派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a37a6816fea3ded05ff74805751e77a038d40a9e","tid":2324855,"uid":54975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:35:09.000Z","msg":"喂口交部話支那好開心生活好滿意㗎嗰<br />\n口徑一致啲啦"},{"pid":"66db864e366346f2f858ddcb1e46efe4ee5a11e1","tid":2324855,"uid":137480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41a50377dff46ee63e9a80d7c9018ba103e9fa90","tid":2324855,"uid":109124,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T08:53:29.000Z","msg":"Cyberpunk 2020 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:38:26.000Z","msg":"小心銀手強尼去放炸彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfd5841849d9670080d453337b10a40d628e1b31","tid":2324855,"uid":155815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:38:54.000Z","msg":"cyberpunk<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f7f6d8213239eb09a32eb0d4edfcead41c28cd5","tid":2324855,"uid":11447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:43:54.000Z","msg":"死咗就唔會有情緒病<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff051c749af369be3f1672fcd7cfa9872c25c7ef","tid":2324855,"uid":195380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:44:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後可以用Shot Riser變身"},{"pid":"5b35a0fb5662d8294c5b7443765083444fa40c69","tid":